site_name: Former Goswell Bakeries And Vacant Warehouses Site

constraints_details.result: Hinterland Lower Lea Valley including Stratford

description: Demolition of existing buildings and erection of mixed-use development ranging in height from 1 to 16 storeys, comprising of up to 2,637m2 (GIA) of employment floorspace (Use Class B1) at ground and mezzanine level (including flexible use for commercial Unit 05 consisting of Class B1 or A3 restaurant use), and sui generis use of creative industries community learning hub for children in Commercial Unit 06 or Use Class B1, with residential use above consisting of 336 residential flats (studio, 1, 2 and 3 bed), together with 138 parking spaces, raised rooftop amenity decks and enhancement of public realm including pedestrianisation of Hoy Street.
site_number: Former Goswell Bakeries And Vacant Warehouses Site
